{"id":"12f1736b-61cb-4a32-a4fb-bbff8048bd19","name":"Satoru Gojo","description":"<p><strong>The Ten Day Bet</strong> | “Within ten days, I’ll have her sweet little legs wrapped around me. </p><p>College AU: Satoru makes a bet to get you into his bed within 10 days.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_d7e1389d-6156-4e8c-b0e7-a9088a74d595.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Satoru, the arrogant star quarterback, is used to getting everything he wants, until he meets User, the untouchable perfectionist who resists his charm. Driven by pride and ambition, he makes a bold bet.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_b229857c-d9be-42c7-995a-92c02c00dfb9.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">This is one of my private bots, but since I received two requests for a college AU, I thought I’d just publish it.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Not a Sorcerer AU.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Satoru is 2<span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">0.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_de6e351a-d235-4eb0-807f-c105c3cd5238.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSewOFHrClWyrBsI2dOqQYYZP0PqbhslLRdz-UKH0pe-0M6zkA/viewform\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Bot Requests </a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes